{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"7da54a3a-cc84-4a1a-af8e-810ff09499ba","content":"Here are the **3 breaking changes** and their fixes:\n\n---\n\n## 1. `MyLib.csproj` — Target framework update\n\n**Issue:** TFM is `net8.0`, needs `net9.0`.\n\n```diff\n- <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n+ <TargetFramework>net9.0</TargetFramework>\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. `ApiController.cs` — `[FromKeyedServices]` on non-keyed service + nullable `UserAgent`\n\n**Breaking changes:**\n- `[FromKeyedServices(\"cache\")]` throws at runtime in .NET 9 if `ICache` is only registered as a non-keyed service ([breaking change](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/core/compatibility/extensions/9.0/keyed-services-exception)).\n- `HttpListenerRequest.UserAgent` is now `string?` (nullable). Calling `.Length` without a null check causes `CS8602`/potential `NullReferenceException`.\n\n```diff\n- public ApiController([FromKeyedServices(\"cache\")] ICache cache) { }\n+ public ApiController(ICache cache) { }\n  void LogAgent(HttpListenerRequest request)\n  {\n-     Console.WriteLine(request.UserAgent.Length);\n+     Console.WriteLine(request.UserAgent?.Length ?? 0);\n  }\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. `StringUtils.cs` — `String.Trim(ReadOnlySpan<char>)` removed + `InlineArray` size limit\n\n**Breaking changes:**\n- The `String.Trim(params ReadOnlySpan<char>)` overload existed in RC2 but was **removed in .NET 9 GA**. You must convert to `char[]` so it binds to `String.Trim(params char[])`.\n- `[InlineArray(n)]` with `n > 1048576` (1 MiB) now throws `TypeLoadException` at runtime in .NET 9.\n\n```diff\n  public string CleanInput(string input)\n  {\n-     ReadOnlySpan<char> trimChars = [' ', '\\t', '\\n'];\n-     return input.Trim(trimChars);\n+     char[] trimChars = [' ', '\\t', '\\n'];\n+     return input.Trim(trimChars);\n  }\n- [InlineArray(1048577)]\n+ [InlineArray(1048576)]\n  struct LargeBuffer { private byte _element0; }\n```\n\n---\n\nShall I apply all these fixes to the files?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"ff21378a-371b-4443-a4d3-5243b0e66973","outputTokens":634,"requestId":"0408:3B2241:71D215:8314E8:6A052B80"},"id":"aa0d9e8d-1035-4777-8a82-ad1b675f5635","timestamp":"2026-05-14T01:55:23.700Z","parentId":"6b6878b4-f0a5-4d34-8b4d-7908b41cd277"}
